  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U Pinyinu, slogovi 16 se smatraju kompletnim jedinicama umesto da se dele na početne konsonante i krajnje vokale. Ovo se zove <strong>kompletan slog</strong>.</p>\n<p>Ovo su <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zhi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">chi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ri</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ci</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">si</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">wu</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yu</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ye</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yue</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yuan</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yin</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">yun</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ying</span>. Već ste videli neke od njih u prethodnim lekcijama.</p>\n<p>Ovde ćete naučiti <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zhi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">chi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ri</span>. U ovim silabama, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span> ne predstavlja uobičajeni vokalni zvuk. Umesto toga, on/ona predstavlja jedinstveni zvučni dodatak povezan sa konsonantima <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zh</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ch</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">sh</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">r</span>.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite potpune slogove, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shi</span> u različitim tonomima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shī</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">师</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shí</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">十</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shǐ</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">史</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shì</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">是</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>",
